{"tid":2045082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍駐港部隊組織搏擊集訓    增官兵快速制敵能力","createTime":"2020-05-31T14:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T14:41:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6816e19d8216b42177da0cf7a0bb92c906e02624","tid":2045082,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2Cb0H6ZLj8WigAzO7A8v3A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/19f97db3143ff1f0270ae18d9768f87d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2Cb0H6ZLj8WigAzO7A8v3A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F19f97db3143ff1f0270ae18d9768f87d&h=c8f5d500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=3cc58548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】解放軍駐香港部隊周日（31日）透過微博發布宣傳片，顯示了某旅組織搏擊骨幹集訓，提升官兵處突應變、快速制敵能力。<br />\n<br />\n片段顯示，參與搏擊集訓的官兵被分成兩隊進行真打實練的對戰，以提升快速制敵能力。集訓隊副隊長楊偉帥表示，地方的搏擊訓練主要是打記分，以輸贏為主，但他們的訓練是以實戰為主。教練員喬康則介紹，這次訓練主要分拳、腿、摔，其中拳法注重的是人員的靈活，還有力量和速度，而快摔時講究更快更準。<br />\n<br />\n楊偉帥進一步稱，戰士在通過集訓後，能更堅韌、更果敢，且拚搏、奮力，制服對方的血性更濃，執行特殊任務時能夠堅韌不屈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xLRw1apU0K7JT7O0xgDrHA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/27827097946e9da650fc75c9ec807f51\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxLRw1apU0K7JT7O0xgDrHA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F27827097946e9da650fc75c9ec807f51&h=bad14889&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3408062188a2e3f787d5a09d98478a674dffd86","tid":2045082,"uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,